Name: overview-sales
Label: Overview Sales

Components.Query:
select count(ds2.Id) as value, 
(case when ds2.TypeId = 2 then 'SEA'
when ds2.TypeId = 3 then 'AIR'
when ds2.TypeId = 4 then 'TRUCKING'
when ds2.TypeId = 5 then 'LOGISTICS'
end) name
from Inquiry ds2
where (ds2.TypeId in (2,3,4,5) and ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}'  and ds2.InsertedDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.InsertedDate < '{ToDate}')
group by ds2.TypeId

select count(ds2.Id) as value, 
(case when ds2.TypeId = 2 then 'SEA'
when ds2.TypeId = 3 then 'AIR'
when ds2.TypeId = 4 then 'TRUCKING'
when ds2.TypeId = 5 then 'LOGISTICS'
end) name
from Inquiry ds2
where (ds2.TypeId in (2,3,4,5) and ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}' and ds2.BookingLocalId is not null  and ds2.InsertedDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.InsertedDate < '{ToDate}')
group by ds2.TypeId

SET NOCOUNT ON;
WITH RevenueCostProfit AS (
    SELECT 
        sm.CustomerId as VendorId,
        SUM(sm.ActualCostUSD) AS ActualCostUSD,
        SUM(sm.ActualRevenueUSD) AS ActualRevenueUSD,
        SUM(sm.ActualProfitUSD) AS ActualProfitUSD
    FROM Shipment sm
    JOIN Shipment s on sm.ParentId = s.Id
    WHERE sm.ParentId is not null and sm.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}' and s.IsComplete = 1 and sm.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and sm.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY sm.CustomerId
),
Revenue1 AS (
    SELECT 
        sf.VendorId,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'VND' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateVND, 1) END) AS ActualRevenueLocal,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'USD' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateUSD, 1) END) AS ActualRevenueUSD
    FROM ShipmentFee sf
    JOIN Shipment sm on sf.ShipmentId = sm.Id
    JOIN Shipment s on sm.ParentId = s.Id
    WHERE sf.TypeId = 1 and sf.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}' and s.IsComplete = 1 and sm.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and sm.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY sf.VendorId
),
Cost1 AS (
    SELECT 
        sf.VendorId,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'VND' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateVND, 1) END) AS ActualCostLocal,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'USD' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateUSD, 1) END) AS ActualCostUSD
    FROM ShipmentFee sf
    JOIN Shipment sm on sf.ShipmentId = sm.Id
    JOIN Shipment s on sm.ParentId = s.Id
    WHERE sf.TypeId in (2,3,4) and sf.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}' and s.IsComplete = 1 and sm.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and sm.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY sf.VendorId
),
Revenue2 AS (
    SELECT 
        sf.VendorId,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'VND' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateVND, 1) END) AS ActualRevenueLocal,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'USD' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateUSD, 1) END) AS ActualRevenueUSD
    FROM ShipmentFee sf
    JOIN Shipment sm on sf.ShipmentId = sm.Id
    JOIN Shipment s on sm.ParentId = s.Id
    WHERE sf.TypeId = 1 and sf.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}' and sf.IsPaid = 1 and s.IsComplete = 1 and sm.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and sm.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY sf.VendorId
),
Cost2 AS (
    SELECT 
        sf.VendorId,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'VND' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateVND, 1) END) AS ActualCostLocal,
        SUM(CASE WHEN sf.CurrencyId = 'USD' THEN sf.TotalAmount ELSE sf.TotalAmount * COALESCE(sf.ExchangeRateUSD, 1) END) AS ActualCostUSD
    FROM ShipmentFee sf
    JOIN Shipment sm on sf.ShipmentId = sm.Id
    JOIN Shipment s on sm.ParentId = s.Id
    WHERE sf.TypeId in (2,3,4) and sf.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}' and sf.IsPaid = 1 and s.IsComplete = 1 and sm.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and sm.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY sf.VendorId
)
select
	p.Name as label,
    isnull(r.ActualRevenueUSD,0) as ActualRevenueUSD,
    isnull(r.ActualCostUSD,0) as ActualCostUSD,
    isnull(r.ActualProfitUSD,0) as ActualProfitUSD,
    (isnull(r1.ActualRevenueUSD,0) - isnull(c1.ActualCostUSD,0)) as REUSD,
    (isnull(r2.ActualRevenueUSD,0) - isnull(c2.ActualCostUSD,0)) as PEUSD,
    ((isnull(r1.ActualRevenueUSD,0) - isnull(c1.ActualCostUSD,0)) - (isnull(r2.ActualRevenueUSD,0) - isnull(c2.ActualCostUSD,0))) as REMAINUSD
FROM RevenueCostProfit r
LEFT JOIN Partner p on p.Id = r.VendorId
LEFT JOIN Revenue1 r1 ON p.Id = r1.VendorId
LEFT JOIN Cost1 c1 ON p.Id = c1.VendorId
LEFT JOIN Revenue2 r2 ON p.Id = r2.VendorId
LEFT JOIN Cost2 c2 ON p.Id = c2.VendorId

from Shipment ds2
where ds2.ParentId is not null and ds2.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}' and ds2.ShipmentTypeId = 0 and ds2.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'

select top 1 ds2.TargetUSDCurr as TotalAmount
from [User] ds2
where ds2.Id = '{TokenUserId}'

select count(ds2.Id) as value, 
p.Name as name
from PartnerCare ds2
join Partner p on ds2.PartnerId = p.Id
where ds2.CategoryId is not null and ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}' and ds2.InsertedDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.InsertedDate < '{ToDate}'
group by p.Name

select count(ds2.Id) as value, 
c.Name as name
from PartnerCare ds2
join MasterData c on ds2.CategoryId = c.Id
where ds2.CategoryId is not null and ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}' and ds2.InsertedDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.InsertedDate < '{ToDate}'
group by c.Name

Components.Query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(ds2.Id) AS Total,
    isnull(SUM(CASE WHEN s.IsComplete = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END),0) AS CompletedTotal
FROM Shipment AS ds2
join Shipment s on ds2.ParentId = s.Id
WHERE ds2.ParentId IS NOT NULL and ds2.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
AND ds2.SaleId = '{TokenUserId}'
